reviewText: I think "Quicksand" is very under rated. I was very happy to see that Amazon had made it available. Mickey Rooney is such a good actor! Not merely "Judge Hardy's son" as we are inclined to think-----catch Mickey in a "Midsummer Nights' Dream". Very versitle  actor In spite of the Andy Hardy casting. The second feature--more Andy Hardy but good as always-----I never thought of him as a returning soldier!
